=N'awo mu ne N'adesua=
Wɔwoo Kwame Nkrumah wɔ Nkrɔful wɔ ɛbɔ 21, 1909. Edin a wɔtoo no ne  Francis Nwia-Kofi Ngonloma. ɔkɔɔ Achimota School, Roman Catholic Seminary wɔ Amisano, a ɔsan kyerɛɛ ade wɔ Catholic School wɔ Aɔim. ɔkɔɔ Amɛrika a, ɛhɔ na ɔkɔɔ Lincoln University ne University  of Pennsylvania. Abibisuafo kuw a ɛwɔ Amɛrika ne Kanada sii no Prɛsidɛnt ɛwɔ wɔn kuw ne so.

ɔkɔɔ London, na Ohyiaa George Padmore a ɛhɔ na ɔhyɛɛ Abibiman faahodie ho nhyehyɛe. Sukuupɔn ahorow pii bɔɔ n'aba so wɔ dwuma pa a ɔhyɛɛ ase no.

